{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clear relentless waves of monsters, destroy environments, build defenses, and upgrade your gear to stay alive and free the world from infernal creatures. <br>Holy Shot is a physics-based, top-down action shooter blending rogue-like elements with sheer chaos, where you collect a variety of devastating weapons <br>and powers to face a diverse range of terrifying creatures and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/spiders.gif?t=1739566582\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Highlights</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Physics-Based Gameplay:</strong> Destroy the environment around you, blow up entire mountains, and unleash firestorms upon floods of arachnids!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategy &amp; Progression:</strong> Know your enemies and arsenal, create effective strategies, and push further each time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Boss Battles:</strong> Study and defeat unique, challenging bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Diverse Arsenal:</strong> Set up turrets and explosives, use several weapon types, find the best power-up combinations, <br>and escape massive hordes with nuclear blasts and holy rains.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique Visual Style:</strong> Uncover secrets and explore a world filled with angelic and demonic imagery, featuring grotesque and bizarre monsters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/Highligths.gif?t=1739566582\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040180/extras/SpiderFires.gif?t=1739566582\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>